@page "/wiki/demon"
@using PhasmoStatsBlazor.Services

<div class="wiki-container">
	<img src="/Images/GhostIcons/demon.webp" />
	<div class="wiki-text">
		<h1 class="header-text wiki-header">
			Demon
		</h1>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section">
			<div class="grid-split">
				<span class="section-header">Hunting Threshold:</span>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="/Images/SanityIcons/HighSanity.png" />
					<div class="threshold-text">70%</div>
				</div>
				<div class="wiki-info">Normal threshold</div>
			</div>
			<br />
			<div class="grid-split">
				<span></span>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="/Images/SanityIcons/HighSanity.png" />
					<div class="threshold-text">100%</div>
				</div>
				<div class="wiki-info">When using its ability</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section">
			<span class="section-header">Evidences</span>
			<div class="grid-split">
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.ThermoPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text freezing-text">Freezing</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.UvPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text uv-text">UV</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sanity-container">
					<img src="@ItemTierService.BookPath" />
					<div class="evidence-text book-text">Writing</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr />
		<div class="text-section">
			<div class="section-header">Abilities<br /></div>
			<div class="wiki-info">
				The demon can hunt at any sanity when using its ability. There are no conditions for that to happen.
			</div>
			<br />
			<div class="section-header">Hunt</div>
			<div class="wiki-info">
				After smudging a Demon, it is unable to hunt for 60 seconds instead of 90 seconds.
				<br /><br />
				Crucifixes have a 50% larger radius for Demons.
				<br /><br />
				After ending a hunt or being stopped from hunting by a crucifix, the Demon can initiate another hunt after 20 seconds instead of 25 seconds.
			</div>
			<br />
		</div>
	</div>
</div>